Bosch 550cc Injectors – High Performance Injectors

Bosch 550cc Injectors provide peak performance. This is a high performance, high volume racing fuel injector.

These genuine ASNU supplied Bosch 550cc Injectors are able to function at high fuel pressures and don’t exhibit the high fuel pressure handling problems found with many other high flow high-impedance injectors.

These flow at 52lbs/hr at 3 Bar (43.5 PSI) making use of a 6 orifice wide split cone spray pattern, perfect for high power Modified and OEM applications.
